---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Bienvenue — Pokévendre Pro" description="Ton profil de revendeur est prêt. Découvre ton diagnostic personnalisé." ogImage="/images/og-merci.jpg" hideCta>

<canvas id="confetti-canvas" style="position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9998;"></canvas>
<canvas id="profile-particles-canvas" style="position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;pointer-events:none;z-index:2;"></canvas>

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-16 px-4 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <div id="bg-glow-1" class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full blur-[120px] transition-colors duration-1000"></div>
    <div id="bg-glow-2" class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/3 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full blur-[100px] transition-colors duration-1000"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-2xl w-full relative z-10 text-center">
    <div class="mb-8 reveal-scale">
      <div id="check-circle" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto shadow-lg transition-all duration-700" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(34,197,94,0.2),rgba(139,92,246,0.2));border:2px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.4);">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-green-400 check-anim" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay:100ms">
      <span class="retro-badge mb-4 inline-block">Profil déverrouillé 🔓</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-2 reveal" style="transition-delay:200ms">
      Bienvenue, <span class="neon-text" id="prenom-display">revendeur</span> ! 🎉
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-2 reveal" style="transition-delay:250ms">
      Ton profil <strong class="text-white" id="profil-name-display">est prêt</strong>
    </p>

    <div id="profile-card" class="hidden reveal" style="transition-delay:300ms">
      <div id="profile-card-inner" class="glass-card p-6 sm:p-8 text-left mt-8 mb-8 border transition-all duration-700" style="border-color:rgba(139,92,246,0.2);">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span id="profile-emoji" class="text-4xl"></span>
          <div>
            <h2 id="profile-title" class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-black text-white"></h2>
            <p id="profile-tagline" class="text-sm italic"></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1.5">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Niveau de progression</h3>
            <span id="level-label" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-3 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden relative">
            <div id="level-bar" class="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-1500 ease-out relative overflow-hidden" style="width:0%">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-white/0 via-white/30 to-white/0 animate-shimmer-bar"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between mt-1">
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-[10px]">🌱 Débutant</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-[10px]">⚡ Intermédiaire</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-[10px]">🔥 Avancé</span>
            <span class="text-gray-600 text-[10px]">🚀 Expert</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Ce qui te définit</h3>
          <div id="profile-traits" class="space-y-2"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-5">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-green-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💪 Tes forces</h3>
            <div id="profile-strengths" class="space-y-1"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-red-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">⚠️ À surveiller</h3>
            <div id="profile-weaknesses" class="space-y-1"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="advice-box" class="rounded-xl p-4 transition-all duration-700" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2);">
          <p id="profile-advice" class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed"></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay:400ms">
      <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-6">Ce qui t'attend maintenant 👇</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10 stagger-children">
        <div id="step1-card" class="glass-card card-glow p-5 text-left border transition-all duration-700" style="border-color:rgba(139,92,246,0.15);">
          <div id="step1-icon" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm mb-3 transition-all duration-700" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.2);color:#a78bfa;">1</div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm mb-1">📧 Vérifie ta boîte mail</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Ton profil détaillé arrive dans les 5 prochaines minutes. Vérifie tes spams si besoin.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card card-glow p-5 text-left">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 font-black text-sm mb-3">2</div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm mb-1">🎯 Applique la méthode</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Suis le plan d'action personnalisé adapté à ton profil pour tes premières reventes rentables.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card card-glow p-5 text-left">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 font-black text-sm mb-3">3</div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm mb-1">📈 Refais le quiz dans 30 jours</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Mesure ta progression et vois comment ton profil évolue avec la pratique.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="share-section" class="reveal" style="transition-delay:500ms">
      <div class="glass-card p-6 text-center mb-8 border transition-all duration-700" style="border-color:rgba(139,92,246,0.15);">
        <p class="text-white font-bold text-sm mb-1">🔗 Partage ton résultat</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-4">Envoie ce quiz à un revendeur qui en a besoin</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 max-w-sm mx-auto">
          <input id="share-url" type="text" readonly class="flex-1 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-gray-300 text-xs outline-none focus:border-purple-500 transition" />
          <button id="copy-btn" class="btn-neon ripple !py-2 !px-4 !text-xs whitespace-nowrap" onclick="copyShareLink()">
            <span id="copy-btn-text">Copier</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="copy-feedback" class="text-green-400 text-xs mt-2 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300">&#10003; Lien copié !</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA RESERVATION -->
    <div id="cta-section" class="reveal" style="transition-delay:600ms">
      <div class="glass-card p-6 sm:p-8 text-center mb-8 border-2 transition-all duration-700" style="border-color:rgba(34,197,94,0.4);background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(34,197,94,0.05),rgba(139,92,246,0.08));">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-green-400">Places limitées</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-black text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-2">Pokévendre Pro</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Formation complète · Accès à vie · Mises à jour incluses</p>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-5xl font-black text-white">🏋️</span>
        </div>
        <button id="reserve-btn" class="btn-neon ripple text-lg px-10 py-4 w-full sm:w-auto cursor-pointer" onclick="reservePlace()">
          <span id="reserve-btn-text">Réserver ma place →</span>
        </button>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-3">🔒 Réservation gratuite — tu seras prévenu en avant-premier</p>
        <p class="text-amber-400 text-xs mt-1">⏳ Lancement imminent — plus que quelques places disponibles.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay:700ms">
      <a href="/" class="inline-block text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-300 transition text-sm">
        &larr; Retour à l'accueil
      </a>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-6">Pok&eacute;vendre Pro &mdash; Le syst&egrave;me de d&eacute;cision pour revendeurs Pok&eacute;mon</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .check-anim {
    stroke-dasharray: 30;
    stroke-dashoffset: 30;
    animation: checkDraw 0.6s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
  }
  @keyframes checkDraw {
    to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
  }
  .profile-trait-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: #d1d5db;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  .profile-trait-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 7px;
  }
  .strength-item, .weakness-item {
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }
  @keyframes shimmer-bar {
    0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
  }
  .animate-shimmer-bar {
    animation: shimmer-bar 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
